videos.headline: Rutgers' bench fired up after Johnson's layup before halftime
videos.description: Rutgers' Diamond Johnson puts in the layup getting the Rutgers bench on their feet.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Rutgers’ bench fired up after Johnson’s layup before halftime) 2021/03/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: BYU's Graham knocks down clutch 3
videos.description: BYU's Tegan Graham drains the 3-pointer to put the Cougars up 4 with a little over a minute remaining.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (BYU’s Graham knocks down clutch 3) 2021/03/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: BYU upsets Rutgers after back-and-forth fourth quarter
videos.description: BYU and Rutgers battle in the fourth quarter but ultimately the Cougars come up clutch to finish the upset victory.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Highlight (BYU upsets Rutgers after back-and-forth fourth quarter) 2021/03/22 ESHEET
